Name: Blend Coffee and Wine

Name: Blend Coffee and Wine

Name: Blend Coffee and Wine

Name: Blend Coffee and Wine

Name: Blend Coffee and Wine
Review Text: Amazing place with the most friendly employees. I arranged a small party to celebrate my wedding and everything was perfect and exactly as we discussed it in advance. Me and my friends had so much fun. I definitely recommend it even for just a coffee. The atmosphere is very cosy and relaxing.

Name: Blend Coffee and Wine
Review Text: Very cosy place with good-looking interior. Could never work out the idea of this place though: it has great wines but it closes at 6 or 8 at night which is too early. It opens too early in the morning at 8 but breakfast/brunch is mediocre and overpriced.

Name: Blend Coffee and Wine
Review Text: Nice service and somehow cozy, even with that mediocre interior. Will keep going.

Name: Blend Coffee and Wine
Review Text: Good coffee, great location (lots of seating, both indoor and outdoor). They sell delicious pastel de nata and staff is always extremely friendly!

Name: Blend Coffee and Wine
Review Text: Had the Memphis style BBQ rib-meat, which was very tender, excellently garnished and with a luxurious sauce. Also had lunch there once which was also great. Good selection of wine and very friendly staff. An inconspicuous place with excellent food!

Name: Blend Coffee and Wine
Review Text: Espresso is nice, but one of the most expensive around, they charged 4,25 for a doppio.

Name: Blend Coffee and Wine
Review Text: A really cool spot with a lovely terrace by the water. Soup and toast ok, but the Caesar salad was kind of light (even for a small eater). Service was totally nice.

Name: Blend Coffee and Wine
Review Text: Good place for drinks and lunch. Nice atmosphere, wilde variety of wines,lunch possibilities. Sunny terrace and acceptabele prices. A spot in Amsterdam east i would recommend.

Name: Blend Coffee and Wine
Review Text: Food was tasty but serving sizes are quite small at lunch - the Ribs with BBQ sauce was tiny (but yummy) but it think that was because they cut he meat off the bones. Tasty iced tea and iced latte.
